{"thig2.4:0.1":"Therigatha 2.4 ","thig2.4:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thig2.4:0.3":"Addhakasitherigatha ","thig2.4:1.1":"“Yava kasijanapado, ","thig2.4:1.2":"sunko me tatthako ahu; ","thig2.4:1.3":"Tam katva negamo aggham, ","thig2.4:1.4":"addhenaggham thapesi mam. ","thig2.4:2.1":"Atha nibbindaham rupe, ","thig2.4:2.2":"nibbindanca virajjaham; ","thig2.4:2.3":"Ma puna jatisamsaram, ","thig2.4:2.4":"sandhaveyyam punappunam; ","thig2.4:2.5":"Tisso vijja sacchikata, ","thig2.4:2.6":"katam buddhassa sasanan”ti. ","thig2.4:3.1":"… Addhakasi theri …. "}